{
  "stem": "4570.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I thought, no, I'd-- I better take that with me, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went into the showers with all my other friends, and we didn't know that the showers can be gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we were not surprised when the water came, because we didn't know about anything else.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody knew about Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So after we were showered, we never went back where our clothes was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We went out on the other side naked in September, wet, naked.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we were given little-- one piece of cloth like, let's say, like a waitress uniform or something and those Dutch shoes that the Dutch people, the country people, wear.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we were hoarded into this big barrack.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it had the three- tier beds.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh, no, no, no-- before, our hair was cut.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Before we went into the accommodation, we, we were again standing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were Slovakian girls.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were-- the were cutting our hair.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was so angry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had this long hair.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in front of me was, again, a beautiful Hungarian woman-- black hair, blue eyes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She was so beautiful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Didn't look Jewish at all, not that Jews-- Jews are also very beautiful.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But-- and she was-- when the woman came with the clippers, this elegant, gorgeous woman took off a wig and put it down.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER] And I just couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So then later, many-- after nearly at the end of the war, I ask her about the wig.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I just couldn't believe it that she was so religious that she wore a wig.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyhow, they cut all-- my all pubic, under the arm, and our hair off.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, then we went into the barracks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was so cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were 10 on one of those wooden things.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
